            <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            <div class="faq-grid">
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>üì∏ How accurate is the AI food analysis?</h3>
                    <p>Our AI provides estimates based on visual analysis and typical serving sizes. For exact nutritional values, we recommend checking food packaging or using manual entry for precision.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>üîê Is my health data secure?</h3>
                    <p>Absolutely! All data is encrypted both in transit and at rest. We never sell your personal information. Your health data belongs to you.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>üì± Can I use StatsKey offline?</h3>
                    <p>Yes! Core features like viewing logged meals and exercises work offline. AI analysis and cloud sync require an internet connection.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>üçé How do I sync with Apple Health?</h3>
                    <p>Go to Settings ‚Üí Integrations ‚Üí Apple Health. Grant permissions for the specific data types you want to sync. You can change these anytime.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>üóëÔ∏è How do I delete my account?</h3>
                    <p>Navigate to Settings ‚Üí Account ‚Üí Delete Account. This will permanently remove all your data from our servers within 30 days.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>üí∞ Is StatsKey free?</h3>
                    <p>Yes! Core features are completely free. We may offer optional premium features in the future, but the essential tracking tools will always be free.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>üîÑ How does cloud sync work?</h3>
                    <p>When you sign in with Apple or Google, your data automatically syncs across all your devices. Changes sync within seconds when online.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>üìä Can I export my data?</h3>
                    <p>Yes! Go to Settings ‚Üí Data ‚Üí Export to download all your nutrition and fitness data in a standard format.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
