            <div class="issue-list">
                <div class="issue">
                    <h4>‚ö†Ô∏è Camera not working</h4>
                    <p><strong>Solution:</strong> Go to iPhone Settings ‚Üí StatsKey ‚Üí Enable Camera access. You may need to restart the app after granting permission.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="issue">
                    <h4>‚ö†Ô∏è HealthKit data not syncing</h4>
                    <p><strong>Solution:</strong> Check Settings ‚Üí Privacy ‚Üí Health ‚Üí StatsKey and ensure all desired permissions are enabled. Then force-close and reopen StatsKey.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="issue">
                    <h4>‚ö†Ô∏è Can't sign in</h4>
                    <p><strong>Solution:</strong> Ensure you have a stable internet connection. For Apple Sign-In issues, check Settings ‚Üí Sign in with Apple. For Google, ensure you're using a valid Google account.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="issue">
                    <h4>‚ö†Ô∏è Food not recognized</h4>
                    <p><strong>Solution:</strong> Try taking a clearer photo with good lighting. You can also use text entry to describe the food, or manually add nutritional information.</p>
